metadata.name: SZN1 OG
metadata.description: This token is for collectors & listeners of The Steady Compass, a video podcast powered by Quezt. It is titled "SZN1 OG" to represent early supporters of the show. The things this token guarantees for holders is subject to change as the show & community grows. This approach is for folks interested in a long journey, similar to that of life's journey. Only 1000 Editions will be available.
